 \sin z=\frac{e^{iz}-e^{-iz}}{2i}=\frac{u-u^{-1}}{2i}=\frac{u^2-1}{2iu}, 
 \sin z=1 \iff \frac{u^2-1}{2iu}=1 \iff u^2-2iu-1=0 \iff (u-i)^2=0 \iff u-i=0, 
